      "id": "ea243807_301446c4",
      "file_path": ".github/workflows/gerrit-required-verify.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 129,
      "message": "The reason for still needing the info-yaml-verify is that the `needs` clause tells the job what it has to wait for before it can run. We absolutely have to have the voting wait on all jobs.",
